":"c48797585d9fb7ffe0d412861b96d4f169229828","tid":803252,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecefb121619a1760d2b405623f472a4ea2cf44b4","tid":803252,"uid":196719,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"我坐咩位你都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608dcf5622c1bcdaa63ccb0260ea9b12d8df17b7","tid":803252,"uid":28624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ecefb121619a1760d2b405623f472a4ea2cf44b4","tid":803252,"uid":196719,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"我坐咩位你都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:10:12.000Z","msg":"咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c90b3fb608650d40f9e52438e6cb0ad4455097","tid":803252,"uid":131345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"上車我係咪知你要早落呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如上車同司機講邊度落 叫佢劃撚埋位啦好冇"},{"pid":"25c9026146f2dc53a656cfaf7cfcf5ce91c8a3ee","tid":803252,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"咁如果入面個位本身有人坐<br />\n只不過係你上車前佢咁啱落車呢<br />\n你又要屌坐出面嗰個唔坐入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0737b278b9faf4cdafcf3e9e76e30cc4819cf93f","tid":803252,"uid":7431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"唔想有人坐隔離囉<br />\n當無雙人位局住要坐人隔離時你正常都唔會專登坐入去窗口位掛<br />\n當然早落都係其中一個原因，但我覺得前者係大部分人既原因，因為自私啲"},{"pid":"44a603eed9a1353cd5445ba3ef2ddf556d920bba","tid":803252,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"咁有d人知自己係遲落<br />\n甚至總站落<br />\n都要坐入面<br />\n係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb63cc61f6be681cb5f0b286f7148670f08061b","tid":803252,"uid":94501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"與其話好笑，不如說on居，不過係真人真事。。。。<br />\n16座小巴，人人都坐過。有一d人好快落車，會坐兩個位既走廊位。<br />\n等後入黎既人坐近窗果個位。。。<br />\n<br />\n咁有一日，有條友仔又早早坐底左0係走廊位，拎住d野咁la。。。<br />\n最後有位大叔上車，得番果條友仔隔離果個近窗位，<br />\n大叔走埋去，企左一陣，同果條友仔互相對峙左一陣。。。<br />\n<br />\n氣氛好似好陰沈咁，大家都知大叔唔想坐入去，同果條友仔唔想讓之間既心理戰架la，好多人都試過架la我相信。。。<br />\n<br />\n突然氣氛一轉。。。<br />\n大叔突然話: &ldquo;我好快樂。。&quot; (ha，我眼都突出黎，做乜野咁快樂，企響度真係咁快樂???。。。)<br />\n<br />\n正當我以為對話到此為止，對峙再繼續既時候。。。<br />\n<br />\n之後大叔又加多句 : &ldquo;我好難過。。&quot; (我心諗，做乜野咁感性，又快樂又難過，唔通辦精神病迫條友仔就範。。??。。。)<br />\n<br />\n之後見到果條友仔就坐入一格，去左近窗 果個位，<br />\n個大叔就坐走廊位la。。。。 (大叔戰術成功左?!?!?!?)<br />\n<br />\n係咪好on居呢我。。。。。<br />\n之後我諗諗下先知個大叔講乜。。<br />\n第一句佢係話。。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我好快落&quot; (落車)。。。<br />\n之後見條友仔唔郁，再加多句。<br />\n&ldquo;我好難過。&quot; (好難行過去)。。<br />\n條友仔先坐入一格。。。<br />\n我無言！"},{"pid":"9fa41343bc56149cb3ae121baa5adb705b36c032","tid":803252,"uid":212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"坐出面最大原因係好撚驚d肥佬坐係隔離,痴撚住哂"},{"pid":"45d785dfff9da5edc55becd85a429249d207b2f6","tid":803252,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"有時坐出面d人見到人地拎住一袋二袋<br />\n都係唔會坐入去讓人<br />\n搞到好麻煩"},{"pid":"5e16ea86170324a0df57719e235f1822bb60c17f","tid":803252,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4c5a7dcde91a959fa43bac9a4fd837b2d3a9f0","tid":803252,"uid":74272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"樓主搭的士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3ed723e983af6791769019359dace026408927","tid":803252,"uid":200861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:55:17.00